text: Besarta Hisenaj (born 21 October 1998) is a German–Kosovan footballer who plays as a midfielder for Hessen Wetzlar and the Kosovo women's national team. ==Career== Hisenaj has been capped for the Kosovo national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Kosovan women's footballers Category:Kosovo women's international footballers Category:German women's footballers Category:German people of Kosovan descent
